This project includes the following components under MIT License:

üöÄ Core Components:
- FastAPI backend with 8 financial data APIs (main.py)
- React TypeScript frontend with modern UI
- Portfolio analysis engine with Fear & Greed Index
- Real-time market data aggregation system
- Risk assessment and AI insights algorithms
- Comprehensive sector analysis (550+ stocks across 11 sectors)

üé® User Interface:
- React-based web application with TypeScript
- Progressive Web App (PWA) support
- Electron desktop app configuration
- Emerald/purple gradient design system
- Interactive charts and real-time data visualization
- Responsive design for mobile and desktop

üìà Financial Data Integration:
- Alpha Vantage API integration
- Twelve Data API integration
- Finnhub API integration
- Polygon.io API integration
- FRED Economic Data API integration
- CoinGecko cryptocurrency data
- Yahoo Finance integration
- World Bank economic indicators

üîß Technical Features:
- Auto-updating data cache system (13-minute intervals)
- Falling stocks monitoring (2-minute intervals)
- Background data processing and redundancy
- Comprehensive error handling and API fallbacks
- Rate limiting and performance optimization

üì± App Deployment:
- Progressive Web App (PWA) manifest and service worker
- Electron desktop application setup
- Docker containerization ready
- Cloud deployment configurations (Vercel, Heroku, AWS)
- Cross-platform compatibility (Windows, macOS, Linux)

